# Spaceship Titanic Logistic Regression Deployment

This project builds a Logistic Regression model for the Spaceship Titanic dataset using:

- scikit-learn Pipeline
- ColumnTransformer
- OrdinalEncoder
- Streamlit app deployment

## Project Structure

```text
